114
00:04:15,689 --> 00:04:19,180
A war isn’t the same as a parade.

115
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:20,570
And the history of the PLA is not,

116
00:04:20,570 --> 00:04:21,910
shall we say,

117
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:23,750
the stuff of legend.

118
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,530
Ninety years ago on August 1,

119
00:04:25,530 --> 00:04:26,530
