120
00:04:26,530 --> 00:04:28,340
set up a guerrilla force called

121
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:29,780
the People’s Liberation Army—

122
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:30,920
the PLA.

123
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:34,160
