124
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:37,030
and then pretty much sat out World War II.

125
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:38,530
It let the Chinese army controlled

126
00:04:38,530 --> 00:04:42,420
by the KMT government fight the Japanese.

127
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:43,420
After the war,

128
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:45,110
the PLA started a civil war

129
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:48,090
by attacking the weakened KMT army.

130
00:04:48,090 --> 00:04:49,090
It won,

131
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:50,090
forcing the Chinese government

132
00:04:50,090 --> 00:04:52,030
to flee to Taiwan.

133
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:53,590
This is what Mao Zedong meant when he said

134
00:04:53,590 --> 00:04:57,070
the Communist Party “liberated” China.

135
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,980
It was straight out of The Art of War.

136
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:01,460
Let your enemy fight another enemy.

137
