for every 1 American soldier they killed.

150
00:05:30,930 --> 00:05:32,950
But that was just one of many

151
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:35,410
shining victories for the PLA.

152
00:05:35,410 --> 00:05:37,140
There was also the early 1950s

153
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:39,440
