160
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:52,840
But the most damning weakness for the PLA

161
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:55,280
is that it is, and always has been,

162
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:57,590
primarily a political tool,

163
00:05:57,590 --> 00:05:59,490
